{"tid":2491358,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(BBC) 黎智英流淚坦承害怕","createTime":"2021-04-16T08:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T09:14:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0ee55a366377c9913dfb98c13ab13ee163543a","tid":2491358,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:57:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=351544926340540&amp;id=101138131381222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D351544926340540%26id%3D101138131381222&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLYXq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=5eec3ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=351544926340540&amp;id=101138131381222</a><br />\n<br />\nGoodbye HK Hello Billy<br />\n5 小時  &middot; <br />\n<br />\n《BBC肥佬黎被捕前專訪：I do have fear》<br />\n<br />\nBBC今日刊登肥佬黎被捕前專訪，原來BBC記者在他因國安法被捕前，曾貼身追訪了他一段日子，到其家中及辦公室進行訪問。在訪問初期，肥佬黎一如既往地表現出硬漢的本色表示，「他當年來港身無分文，一分一毫都是取之香港。如果他要入獄，他仍過著他有意義的人生。如現在是還債的時候，這就是他的贖罪（redemption)⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n就在他表現得最堅強的一刻，記者問及他會否擔心身邊的家人，身邊至親至愛時，他低首默默無語良久不能說話，然後在硬咽與流眼之中抬頭說：「Yes. I do have fear.」<br />\n<br />\n然後，訪問就以他行將被捕而結束。<strong>無論你認為他是鐵漢、性情中人、犧牲者、不守常規的企業家、抑或是唯利是圖的生意人，無道德底線的傳媒老闆，甚或候判人士和罪犯，我們都應該了知的是：他是一個人⋯⋯</strong><br />\n<br />\n後記：新聞訪問以紀錄片形式拍攝，同時以香港記者採訪新聞角度出發探討。<br />\n傳送門：<br />\nJimmy Lai: The Hong Kong billionaire risking it all by speaking out <a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-56767127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-56767127&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLYXq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=5a456bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-56767127</a><br />\n<br />\n#他是一個人"},{"pid":"2400acd6c0a73f3d3a558f46b775c51732e2c8db","tid":2491358,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ea353938382ae1b3f2a88b96297397cf7b3fea","tid":2491358,"uid":89517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a37caaf9334b36810e49b7bd1f7b75962be366","tid":2491358,"uid":310817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5ef6b35039099b14ea61989263766a3dd6f483","tid":2491358,"uid":43062,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:59:22.000Z","msg":"睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾堅強都好，佢都係一個人嚟"},{"pid":"ac2bc8c6fdd66d5830f11c34effc490e21921f0e","tid":2491358,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e57cbb1ed64b2a4e4d1012118437192ba79918","tid":2491358,"uid":16425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6f7f7155a4d53751f6b8af96b36baaec1c4e42","tid":2491358,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"